reviewText:
Luther Barnes and his family and the Sunset Jubilaires are one of my very favorite groups. They are a great family that really
ministers to your spirit. I have a few more of their recordings and they have just blessed me so much. I had this on VHS
and I'm replacing it with the DVD because my tape has worn out.

Although I thought I ordered a video dvd, it was just a regular audio cd, but I enjoyed it alot. I am a fan of Luther Barnes & the Sunset Jubilaires. This CD lifts my spirits up, especially when I am feeling low. They are a blessing to listen too.
I purchased this cd because i loved Luther Barnes & the Sunset Jubilaires music. I was not disappointed with this cd and it is highly recommended.
